<plot>August 2004. Athens. For ten days the planet focuses on a city. A young Japanese couple come to get married in the Athens Olympics, a Russian returns twenty years later to find his youth's love. A yuppie wants to escape from the Games psychosis, a young girl runs away and seeks a new father. A TV reporter watches her life turn up side down, a provincial girl comes to Athens to watch her athlete-idol. For ten days the planet focuses on a city but there are some stories nobody will see. These are the true miracles of the city!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?254367</url></doc>
